data.comment: The match is underway in Stockholm.
Free kick for Hammarby in their own half.
In the minute 4, Goal! Gustav Ludwigson gives Hammarby a 1-0 lead in Stockholm.
Abdul Khalili with an assist there.
Hammarby take a comfortable 2-0 lead thanks to Aron Johannsson.
In the minute 5, Great play from Abdul Khalili to set up the goal.
Can Mjallby get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Hammarby's half?

Hammarby drives forward and Alexander Kacaniklic gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
Hammarby move into a more comfortable 3-0 lead. Gustav Ludwigson is the scorer with a header!
In the minute 12, Alexander Kacaniklic instrumental with a fine assist.
